The paper is about using Convolutional Neural Networks (ConvNets) for network intrusion detection. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses transfer learning, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves training a model on a dataset and testing it on another dataset, which is a common approach in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV).
